Class TransactionLogsRecovery

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.kernel.lifecycle.LifecycleAdapter
      • org.neo4j.kernel.recovery.TransactionLogsRecovery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Lifecycle
    public class TransactionLogsRecovery
extends LifecycleAdapter
    This is the process of doing a recovery on the transaction log and store, and is executed at startup of Database.
